data.description: Welcome to this stunning 4 bed, 2.5 bath home located in the heart of Colonial Park. Situated just minutes away from MSU and the walking trail, this property offers the perfect combination of convenience and tranquility. Step inside where you'll be greeted by timeless renovations that blend modern updates with classic charm. The spacious layout includes two living areas, providing ample space for relaxation and entertainment. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this charming property your own!
